{"tid":817472,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個香港人 咁既颱風真係得啖笑","createTime":"2018-09-13T11:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T14:04:33.000Z","uid":147608,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b325abe5f00dc26a380b920b0bf367f93c54d69","tid":817472,"uid":147608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:40:13.000Z","msg":"作為一個香港人 咁既颱風真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈禮拜一要返工有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班打工仔 totally no mood to 捱夜睇掛波 嗱,我又分析下 首先山咩竹,唔好玩啦 酒樓野，減左3號先<br />\n<br />\n超強颱風,,如果係溫黛就有可觀性(順便可以試下力場強度)(不過算啦,下年又會再upgrade) 我真係冇怕過依壇野..力場半力夠WIN,呢度又減3號<br />\n<br />\n講下講下,我連名都唔記得 我地聽天文台9 up下is ok,又3號<br />\n<br />\n加上我地2大屏障 台灣,菲律賓 加上關鍵王屏風樓.. 根本唔會有風,,,,<br />\n<br />\n返工就一定..係睇下掛唔掛到黃雨.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家庇護工場見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手力場..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"b1b1c0ffe2b48ad3e4bcc6668c2ffe738031b778","tid":817472,"uid":29567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"7e5b763399cd92bee28a285652866261fba15f1e","tid":817472,"uid":131686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1b1c0ffe2b48ad3e4bcc6668c2ffe738031b778","tid":817472,"uid":29567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:46:00.000Z","msg":"1999"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"佢ot到癡咗線，原諒佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf9028002949921ab6d8a6ee590ba0c01e94326","tid":817472,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"呢篇都好耐未見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae39b5d1dea1578d8636c8269991173cca362da","tid":817472,"uid":83933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"佮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe01893e9fb8711454acbbe13495940358a2fa0","tid":817472,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:24:11